      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the oil is hot, add the <strong>pork belly pieces</strong>, fatty-side down, to the dish</p><p>Cook, without turning, for 2 min or until golden</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p>",
      "order": 3,
